      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Server / Host Metrics\n\nMonitor infrastructure across your fleet with per-column threshold coloring \u2014 each metric is evaluated independently.\n\n### Features demonstrated\n\n- \ud83d\udd22 **Row numbers** \u2014 sequentially numbered rows\n- \ud83d\udcca **Per-column cell coloring** \u2014 CPU, Memory, and Disk each fire their own thresholds independently. A server with high CPU but low memory shows one red cell and green cells for the rest.\n- \ud83d\udd17 **Clickthrough** \u2014 click any hostname to drill into that host\n- \ud83d\udcc4 **Pagination** \u2014 10 rows per page for large fleets\n- \ud83d\udcd0 **Column width hints** \u2014 the Last Updated column has an explicit width\n\n[Open Overview \u2192](/d/dt-server-metrics-overview)",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        }
      },
      "targets": []
    },
